---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="About Us">

  <style>
    /* Reuse the high-tech grid background */
    .bg-grid {
      background-size: 40px 40px;
      background-image: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px),
                        linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
    }
    
    /* Reveal Animation */
    .reveal {
      animation: reveal 0.8s ease-out forwards;
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
    }
    @keyframes reveal {
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
  </style>

  <section class="pt-48 pb-20 px-6 bg-slate-50 bg-grid border-b border-slate-200">
    <div class="max-w-[1000px] mx-auto text-center">
      
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-white border border-slate-200 text-slate-600 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-8 shadow-sm reveal">
        Est. 2020 ‚Ä¢ Nairobi, Kenya
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-8 leading-tight tracking-tight reveal" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
        We represent the new standard of <br />
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-700 to-indigo-600">African Engineering.</span>
      </h1>
      
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-500 mb-12 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto font-normal reveal" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
        Talkin Tech is an infrastructure company. We build the hidden engines that power payments, logistics, and data for the continent's most ambitious organizations.
      </p>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 px-6 bg-slate-900 text-white overflow-hidden relative">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-blue-600/20 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto relative z-10">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Built for High Volume.</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
            Most local software crashes when it hits 1,000 users. Ours is just getting started. We architect systems designed to handle millions of transactions without blinking.
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-8 border-t border-slate-800 pt-8">
            <div>
              <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-1">15M+</div>
              <div class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest">Requests / Month</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-500 mb-1">99.99%</div>
              <div class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest">Uptime SLA</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-950 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 p-8 shadow-2xl relative">
          <div class="flex gap-2 mb-6">
            <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500 animate-pulse"></div>
            <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-slate-800"></div>
            <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-slate-800"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-xs font-mono text-slate-500 mb-1">
              <span>Cluster A (Nairobi)</span>
              <span class="text-green-500">Online</span>
            </div>
            <div class="h-2 bg-slate-900 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
               <div class="h-full w-[40%] bg-blue-600 rounded-full"></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-xs font-mono text-slate-500 mb-1 pt-2">
              <span>Cluster B (Mombasa)</span>
              <span class="text-green-500">Online</span>
            </div>
            <div class="h-2 bg-slate-900 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
               <div class="h-full w-[25%] bg-indigo-600 rounded-full"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-xs font-mono text-slate-500 mb-1 pt-2">
              <span>Database Replicas</span>
              <span class="text-blue-500">Syncing...</span>
            </div>
            <div class="h-2 bg-slate-900 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
               <div class="h-full w-[80%] bg-slate-700 rounded-full animate-pulse"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-32 px-6 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900">Our DNA</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-500 mt-4">The principles that guide every line of code we write.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        
        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-6">üîí</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Security is not optional.</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            We deal with financial data. Every system we build has bank-grade encryption and audit logs by default.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-6">üåç</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Context Matters.</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            We optimize for slow 3G networks, integrate M-Pesa natively, and build offline-first capability for remote areas.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-blue-600 p-8 rounded-3xl text-white">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-6">‚ö°</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Speed Wins.</h3>
          <p class="text-blue-100 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Slow software loses customers. We obsess over milliseconds, database indexing, and caching strategies.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 px-6 bg-slate-50 border-t border-slate-200">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-12">Leadership</h2>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-slate-200 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
               <div class="w-full h-full bg-slate-300"></div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900">Elijah Onsongo</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-blue-600 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Founder & CEO</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-6 text-slate-500 text-sm">
            Full-stack engineer with 6+ years experience building financial systems in East Africa.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-slate-200 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
               <div class="w-full h-full bg-slate-300"></div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900">Head of Product</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-blue-600 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Engineering</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-6 text-slate-500 text-sm">
            Systems Architect specializing in high-availability cloud infrastructure and APIs.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-slate-200 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
               <div class="w-full h-full bg-slate-300"></div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900">Head of Operations</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-blue-600 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Client Success</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-6 text-slate-500 text-sm">
            Ensuring our partners receive 24/7 support and seamless deployment experiences.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 px-6 bg-white text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">Ready to work with the best?</h2>
    <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-slate-900 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-blue-600 transition-colors shadow-lg hover:shadow-blue-600/20">
      Contact Our Team
    </a>
  </section>

</MainLayout>